Style/AccessModifierDeclarations.description:
Description

Checks style of how access modifiers are used.
Style/AccessModifierDeclarations.option:
This rule supports the following parameters in your configuration:

EnforcedStyle: group (type: str)
SupportedStyles: ['inline', 'group'] (type: list)
AllowModifiersOnSymbols: True (type: bool)
AllowModifiersOnAttrs: True (type: bool)
AllowModifiersOnAliasMethod: True (type: bool)
